---item_39 Risky Business---
Type :: Equippable
Slot :: Active
Icon :: items_723
Gun Definition :: [[Risky Business]]
Rarity :: Legendary

On use, absorb 50% of incoming damage for a short period of time. Afterward, charge your next bullet with the damage.

Some folks just like to live on the very edge of reason. Clearly you're one of them.

